graph TD
    A[Open FIFO] --> B{Mode?}
    B -->|FREAD| C[Increment fi_readers]
    B -->|FWRITE| D[Increment fi_writers]
    C --> E[Return 0]
    D --> F[Return 0]

    G[Read from FIFO] --> H{fi_writers == 0 && fi_size == 0?}
    H -->|yes| I[Return 0: EOF]
    H -->|no| J[Copy data to user buffer]
    J --> K[Update fi_head and fi_size]
    K --> L[Return bytes read]

    M[Write to FIFO] --> N{fi_readers == 0?}
    N -->|yes| O[Return EPIPE: no readers]
    N -->|no| P[Copy data from user buffer]
    P --> Q[Update fi_tail and fi_size]
    Q --> R[Return bytes written]
